field.value:
Giving a xml configuration like <component id="sessionFactoryProvider" service='uNhAddIns.IMyFactory, uNhAddIns' type='MyFactory, uNhAddIns'/>
<component id="uNhAddIns.sessionFactory" type="NHibernate.ISessionFactory, NHibernate" factoryId="sessionFactoryProvider" factoryCreate="GetFactory"> <parameters> <factoryId>uNhAddIns</factoryId> </parameters> </component>
Allow a fluent configuration like container .Register(Component .For<ISessionFactory>() .UsingFactory<ISessionFactoryProvider>(service => service.GetFactory("uNhAddIns")));
